  ("npc1_intro_response_1", "Only a fool wouldn't ask you to join my adventuring party."),
  ("npc2_intro_response_1", "I am indeed yes, I lead a brave party of warriors, no land is untreadable for us."),
  ("npc3_intro_response_1", "It is true that war is in my nature but it has to be in this land. What do you know of my work anyway?"),
  ("npc4_intro_response_1", "I have never had an Orc call me {reg33?madame:sir} before."),
  ("npc5_intro_response_1", "An efficient killer is always of use to me?"),
  ("npc6_intro_response_1", "Whichever paths I please, you look like you have trodden many yourself."),
