  ("npc1_backstory_a", "You don't look like much of an adventurer.... mmmm."),
  ("npc2_backstory_a", "Your party interests me."),
  ("npc3_backstory_a", "I enquired when I saw your party enter the town. They say you are a bold warrior and that you are on the lookout for other able warriors to join you."),
  ("npc4_backstory_a", "Yes it seems my lack of orcness never escapes me."),
  ("npc5_backstory_a", "Then Ripnitch the assassin is where you should invest your money."),
  ("npc6_backstory_a", "I have trodden every part of these great lands, I am Mathias Thulmann, Master Witch Hunter."),
  ("npc7_backstory_a", "I am not offering a potion, I am offering my services on the field of battle and also recommending my men."),
  ("npc8_backstory_a", "Ah yes, you got me. I am not usually this rusty but I am feeling a bit peaky after eating all of Skeezles goats cheese, it has put me off my game."),
  ("npc9_backstory_a", "I am a knight but I do not follow any soft, repressive codes such as chivalry and honour. All they do is trick a man into being obedient and to restrain all the natural and rightful urges a real man feels."),
  ("npc10_backstory_a", "Grand campaigns usually mean lots of battles and lots of bloodshed which is exactly what I live for."),
  ("npc11_backstory_a", "I don't see why but if you must know my name is Eketi and I am a Commander of the Dark Elf naval fleets."),
  ("npc12_backstory_a", "Skrizzle, skrizzle................. wooooompa.............. Bug is me.................. woooooop."),
  ("npc13_backstory_a", "My name is Sir Aristide, I am a knight from the court of King Leoncouer."),
  ("npc14_backstory_a", "My name is Maephilin, I am a skilled horse archer and I used to patrol the lands of Ellyrion in the Old World looking for enemies so I am good at spotting enemies too."),
  ("npc15_backstory_a", "I am looking for someone to travel with, to explore with and to share stories with and you look like just the kind of companion I am looking for."),
  ("npc16_backstory_a", "I have no story really. I have been mocked and ridiculed my whole life. Skeezle is my name."),
  ("npc17_backstory_a", "Well of course I am serious, it is a serious world out there with no room for trivialities."),
  ("npc18_backstory_a", "Adventure, fun, the thrill of the chase, riding on the open sea in the face of danger that is what is important to me."),
  ("npc19_backstory_a", "My name is Nakwatcha and I am completely lost."),
  ("npc20_backstory_a", "I am just having a quick break from my treasure hunts, give myself a chance to splash the riches I manage to acquire."),
  ("npc21_backstory_a", "I am sorry fellow, I thought you were another punter coming over to thank me for making my beloved brew."),
  ("npc22_backstory_a", "I am about as dangerous as they come. Like my race I am on a path of destruction right now and no one will stand in my way."),
  ("npc23_backstory_a", "I used to be a seafaring man you know, back when I used to leave port on a regular basis. Not enough booze out at sea know what I mean Captain, hahahaha. So you find me mostly on land now."),
  ("npc24_backstory_a", "No, but I have tracked your party a number of times as you have travelled throughout the land. I am quite familiar with your movements."),
  ("npc25_backstory_a", "They look like a decent lot but they could use some more training."),
  ("npc26_backstory_a", "I am no mercenary and you are lucky I don't break you in two for saying so. Like most Ogres I used to be a mercenary when I was younger but I have moved on to greater things since then."),
  ("npc27_backstory_a", "Two hours, I killed a guard at the gate for asking for a toll to pass. I have had no opportunity since then unfortunately."),
  ("npc28_backstory_a", "That is because I am not a Nehekharan, I am an Imperial Lord or should I say I used to be an Imperial Lord anyway."),
  ("npc29_backstory_a", "I am looking for a leader, someone who will give me fame and fortune."),
