  ("npc1_backstory_b", "Well know this, I am seeking a glorious death through fighting against the mightiest foes. It is my lifes mission but I will not go down easily, it will take a being of legends to send me to my grave. I used to be an engineer before I was disowned by my clan but this is my life now, I seek danger and maybe I will seek it with you."),
  ("npc2_backstory_b", "My name is Felix. I am an adventurer and a poet and I wish to write the tales of the leaders I follow when I retire. I am currently bound to Gotrek but I lost him after a nights heavy drinking. I will go find him soon but in the meantime I would be happy to join your party."),
  ("npc3_backstory_b", "My name is Jalil Najid and I used to be the personal bodyguard for many of my Kingdom's Caliphs. I am a master Janissary and I am famed for never letting an assassin get close enough to my master to get into hand to hand combat. My eyes are sharp and my skill with a bow is unrivalled, if I see you and you are an enemy, then you have but a few seconds to live."),
  ("npc4_backstory_b", "My name is Oggy and I was kicked out of my tribe for my lack of aggression. I was never into breaking bones, just healing them. I am skilled in the arts of healing and medicine but these skills got me no respect back home."),
  ("npc5_backstory_b", "I kill, get high on warpstone and kill some more. Just show me who is the enemy and my blade will see them rot on the soil."),
  ("npc6_backstory_b", "I dedicate my life to the eradication of evil and the banishing of the unholy. I am currently taking a break from a major campaign against the Witch Elves that has been running for years. We drove them out of the Old World and now we have followed them to the New World."),
  ("npc7_backstory_b", "My name is Captain Braganza, leader of the Braganza's Besiegers, masters of siege warfare and all wars of attrition. We are by far the best value mercenaries available in the Old World and up until recently we have been in the service of the great Borgio, the highest endorsement a company can get."),
  ("npc8_backstory_b", "I am knowledgeable in all the plant life of these lands and their healing properties. Being a healer is all I have ever wanted to do but my family have sent me out into the world to teach me of the world's dangers and make me more serious apparently."),
  ("npc9_backstory_b", "Goats cheese always does it to me but you know when you you love something so much, you don't even care, totally worth it, even if it has left me red handed."),
  ("npc10_backstory_b", "Since I was born I have desired nothing but to kill and destroy for the Gods who favoured me with the power of transformation. So successful have I been that I have gained my own followers who fear nothing and will fight savagely to their last breath."),
  ("npc11_backstory_b", "Our naval capacity in this part of the world has increased faster than any other race over the last few decades. Very soon only the pirates will be of real concern to us. We are currently building a new  and preparing plans for sea supremacy so I am out of work."),
  ("npc12_backstory_b", "Grizznick, ratatatatatatatata.......................... I like to fight................. booomzoggyzoggy."),
  ("npc13_backstory_b", "I have recently completed a great mission to make safe my people in our home lands. The King made me his greatest champion and gave me a time of leave to pray and to see my family but sooner than I expected I was called back."),
  ("npc14_backstory_b", "Our situation here is not as secure as it used to be. We don't have much land and we are not as dominant on the sea. We are vulnerable in a way we have ever been. Sometimes the seas are too dangerous and we need to travel the whole distance of the land to get word to our brothers and sisters on the continent. This is why I am here."),
  ("npc15_backstory_b", "My name is Abdul Khaliq and I am an an anthropologist and a historian. I live to be educated and to educate others on foreign cultures and of the culture of my great nation Araby. There is alot of misunderstanding and mistrust among races and nations in this world, a misinterpretation can lead to unfair opinions or even war. I hope to be a diplomat when I am older and bring greater understanding to the world."),
  ("npc16_backstory_b", "For most of my life I was weak, beyond weak really but I always wanted to be an assassin and be respected by clan Eshin. I tried to better myself for years in the Old World, I never gave up despite knowing my ability but noone would really help me, and I was always a laughing stock."),
  ("npc17_backstory_b", "You may enjoy a bit of the jovial but when you have lived a life of protecting and serving your people in times like we have had recently you will know why I am as stern as I am. My name is Scarloc and for much of my life I have protected the Laurelorn forest from invaders and trespassers, especially the green skinned kind."),
  ("npc18_backstory_b", "My name is Eleanor Nash and I used to be captain of the Silver Twilight until she was burnt to cinders by the Tomb Kings."),
  ("npc19_backstory_b", "I was chased out of the forest near my home by a family of giant snakes! We are normally used to them but these were so big and they chased me for 3 days."),
  ("npc20_backstory_b", "I used to work for a dungeon adventurers guild but I was so damn unlucky. All kinds of stuff happened to me although I was always able to find a way to turn things around eventually."),
  ("npc21_backstory_b", "The name is Joseph Bugman and I am the master brewer who brews 'Bugman's XXXXXX'. I am sure you know of my work. My brewery is near Karak Hirn although it has only recently been rebuilt."),
  ("npc22_backstory_b", "Lustria is very attractive to the outside world. Many Human, Skaven, Orc and Elf try and steal the relics of our ancestors and the sacred treasures of Sotek."),
  ("npc23_backstory_b", "You know you look like a leader, and I used to be on ships led by great leaders, great pirates who ruled the waves from one end to the other."),
  ("npc24_backstory_b", "My name is Adelyn and I am skilled in the arts of tracking and path finding. My people are so hell bent on creating new machinery and technology to do their work for them but I prefer to use the more natural tools given to me."),
  ("npc25_backstory_b", "My name is Erasmus. I used to be the head pitfighter trainer at the fighting pits in Mordheim. Some of the best fighters in history have been trained in my school. Strength, skill and relentlessness are all qualities I brand onto my students. Don't confuse them with the ones you see in tournaments, I have nothing to do with those incompetent fools."),
  ("npc26_backstory_b", "My name is Uggluk Snaggletooth and I come from a land far to the north of the Chaos wastelands. I was once a mighty bull but now I am an outcast after losing a fight with the tyrant for control of my kingdom."),
  ("npc27_backstory_b", "I was born to kill, ever since I was an infant I discovered the pleasures of smashing the life out of others. Any quest, any adventure, I will take it if it means a chance for a fight."),
  ("npc28_backstory_b", "I liked to go exploring, treasure hunting to further the glory and prestige of the Empire. I wanted to discover new lands and hopefully claim uninhabited land for us on new continents. Sadly for me I went south instead of south west."),
  ("npc29_backstory_b", "I hear rumours that you are that someone."),
