  ("npc1_backstory_c", "But know this, I give everything to the mission at hand, whatever the odds, and whatever the sacrifice! I will not tolerate a leader who does not do the same."),
  ("npc2_backstory_c", "I am handy with a sword though not the best fighter you will ever see. Put me up against the skaven scum and you will see no warrior more determined than me. I can also rouse the camp with a tale or two I tell you."),
  ("npc3_backstory_c", "I left my post recently though as the Caliphs are favouring Sultan's guards over us janissary's as bodyguards nowadays. I am looking for a new master to serve and I think you may be the one I am looking for."),
  ("npc4_backstory_c", "I used to work as a medic in the Blood Bowl leagues but the crowd would rather chant insults at me for my softness rather than at the opposition team. So I left my job and was banished soon after."),
  ("npc5_backstory_c", "You need one such as me yes?."),
  ("npc6_backstory_c", "The difference here is that our intelligence on the Dark Elf land is not as reliable as before so we will now watch and wait rather than continue the assault. If you have a spot in your company for a skilled fighter I could ride with you in the mean time?"),
  ("npc7_backstory_c", "We are now released and my men have parted in order to train and make experience different types of wars. I now offer you my services, as their leader and the finest of our company. Hire me and also hire my troops whenever you can."),
  ("npc8_backstory_c", "Anyway lets just call this even and get back to our business. I would offer you some cheese but it is all gone."),
  ("npc9_backstory_c", "We are also for sale around the taverns of the Old World. If you can afford my men then hire them, that is if you want to win battles. I am available for hire too, the best of them all."),
  ("npc10_backstory_c", "You will find them in the many taverns you will come across on your grand campaigns. They fight for the Gods and for me, if you will truly indulge me in relentless conquest then I may just fight for you."),
  ("npc11_backstory_c", "It won't last forever though and when we are ready to make our move we will control the seas from top to bottom. Nothing will go on without our permission. On pain of death."),
  ("npc12_backstory_c", "Gouge the eye, pluck the beast, gorge upon a greasy feast................. you like pie? Wahahahahahahahahah!"),
  ("npc13_backstory_c", "The King called for a crusade against Araby and the Tomb Kings, both have been gaining in power over the years and he fears that if one gets too powerful then they will invade. We are pre-empting this by striking first. The crusade has been on and off though as fighting there has been harder than we thought. We have made more enemies than we figured and our resources and campaign plans have had to be cancelled and rethought."),
  ("npc14_backstory_c", "My passion is for breeding horses, I breed the best in the whole world and if my kin are to travel quickly here they will need my horses. I have set up 3 stables here which will breed the best stock quickly but I am reluctant to go home in case something goes wrong."),
  ("npc15_backstory_c", "Obviously you will need more than my mind as you are a warrior party after all but I can assure you than I am a good horse archer who can do his fair share on the battlefield."),
  ("npc16_backstory_c", "Then I came to this part of the world and Clan Rictus offered me friendship and training to become a stormvermin. My whole life I only wanted to be Eshin but it was Rictus who took me as their own. I know I am not that strong compared to most but for the first time in my life I can defend myself and be of service to those I wish to help."),
  ("npc17_backstory_c", "Recently our lands have been infested with a dark power, Sylvanian we think although we thought they were destroyed. We have fled to a secret location while rangers such as myself stay on the lookout for a time when it is safe to come back."),
  ("npc18_backstory_c", "I have been moving around from town to town but I am getting bored now of beating up all the men and taking their money at poker. It was fun at the start but now it is old hat. I want a challenge if you know what I mean, I didn't grow up to live the same low key life as these skallywags."),
  ("npc19_backstory_c", "Right now I don't know what to do as I am young and not very experienced. I see safety in numbers so I would like to join your party and do what you do. I would feel a lot safer."),
  ("npc20_backstory_c", "When I first heard about Lustria I was sceptical but when I was told about the riches to be found in the new world I nearly wet myself in excitement. My luck has turned since I started going there and I am not even sure if I will go back underground."),
  ("npc21_backstory_c", "It was destroyed and all my workers killed a while ago by an army of Goblin raiders. I vowed vengeance and I took my war party out to get revenge for this gravest of crimes. We went out and spilt blood but only I returned. So much death, and not even the execution of justice can placate the fury inside of me. I cannot bear to go back to my brewery at the moment as the pain is still too near, my new workers are doing a fine job though and my brew is as good as ever. I will rise against the goblins again, my rangers are currently training in the town tournaments, what a force they will be."),
  ("npc22_backstory_c", "Before it was small excursions, either private or state funded but now the humans are sending whole armies to our land and it poses the greatest threat to our existence."),
  ("npc23_backstory_c", "Sometimes I wish I was back out there having adventures, but, hic, then I remember, hic hic. How comfortable it is in a tavern!"),
  ("npc24_backstory_c", " I have never been much of a fighter but I love to travel and see the world. There is always much war and conflict going on but if you take the time to learn local cultures and customs you can have a peaceful and fulfilling time as a traveller."),
  ("npc25_backstory_c", "I am skilled in the arts of all weapons and I would like to join your company and help train your men into the finest fighters in the field."),
  ("npc26_backstory_c", "Normally losing a fight with a tyrant costs you your life but I managed to escape, albeit in a much weaker state than I was. Now I stay in this part of the world, but one day once I have built up my strength and accumulated enough wealth to afford an army I will return and claim my kingdom for myself."),
  ("npc27_backstory_c", "I saw your army earlier, if you are an adventurer then maybe you could use my strength, speed and agility to destroy your enemies?"),
  ("npc28_backstory_c", "I ended up in Nehekhara, in a Tomb King pyramid. I was excited with what I found but I was foolish and didn't heed the signs to run. I ran into a liche priest who cursed me and turned me in to one of them."),
  ("npc29_backstory_c", "So I travelled around to find you and here you are."),
