  ("npc1_backstory_later", "You again! Either drink and talk, or drink and be silent, either way you'd better grab a tankard."),
  ("npc2_backstory_later", "I have been selling poetry for which men can use to woo a fair maiden, it has been quite lucrative. You would have thought that people would be capable to at least think of something themselves, but I guess not."),
  ("npc3_backstory_later", "I have been looking for work but not many people seem to see the value in a ranged specialist bodyguard. Maybe you are ready to give me work?"),
  ("npc4_backstory_later", "I have tried so hard but still no one wants to hire my talents. Have you found a good healer yet {sir/madame}, if not please do not forget I am here."),
  ("npc5_backstory_later", "If you don't hire me soon my price will only go up."),
  ("npc6_backstory_later", "My offer is still there if you wish to take it?"),
  ("npc7_backstory_later", "If you have sieges to win you know where I am."),
  ("npc8_backstory_later", "Got any cheese?"),
  ("npc9_backstory_later", "You going to hire me or what?"),
  ("npc10_backstory_later", "Grrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrr"),
  ("npc11_backstory_later", "You again, be quick."),
  ("npc12_backstory_later", "Xom xom xom."),
  ("npc13_backstory_later", "Good day to you again traveller, I trust everything is going your way."),
  ("npc14_backstory_later", "If it isn't {playername} once more, you seem to travel nearly as fast as me. I am still looking for some real work, nothing but odd jobs have surfaced recently."),
  ("npc15_backstory_later", "We meet again {playername}, I would still like to join your party so if you have room then please accept me as a companion."),
  ("npc16_backstory_later", "If you need a stormvermin to help clear out your enemies then I am your rat."),
  ("npc17_backstory_later", "Good day, let us have a drink and exchange information."),
  ("npc18_backstory_later", "My new ship won't be built for a while yet, find me a quest you rascal."),
  ("npc19_backstory_later", "Please help me, I don't know what to do."),
  ("npc20_backstory_later", "How you been traveller? I hope you have been as successful as I have."),
  ("npc21_backstory_later", "If you are going to fight any greens kins, no one will fight them harder than me, just tell me where they are."),
  ("npc22_backstory_later", "There have been too many enemies to fight recently, our armies are spread thin."),
  ("npc23_backstory_later", "Hic, hello again, hic."),
  ("npc24_backstory_later", "I have been doing some more travelling and I am thinking of exploring the most hidden places in Lustria. If a better offer comes along though I would not say no."),
  ("npc25_backstory_later", "I hope you change your mind soon about letting me in your party, your troops are still not up to scratch."),
  ("npc26_backstory_later", "I have been moving around feeling a bit sorry for myself, I need to get back my old mentality."),
  ("npc27_backstory_later", "I am a Norse barbarian, ready to take on anyone, any time, any place."),
  ("npc28_backstory_later", "If you see Bastich let him know I am ready for that drinking contest. I used to be a lightweight but now drink just goes straight through me."),
