  ("npc1_backstory_response_1", "You will find all the beer and action you need with me Master Slayer"),
  ("npc2_backstory_response_1", "I can't believe I didn't find you sooner, welcome to my party"),
  ("npc3_backstory_response_1", "You are a specialist and I can use as many specialists in my party as I can find. Join me."),
  ("npc4_backstory_response_1", "Well I could use your exceptional talents in my party."),
  ("npc5_backstory_response_1", "I could use someone as ruthless as you."),
  ("npc6_backstory_response_1", "You are welcome to join us Mathias, we could use some serious fire power."),
  ("npc7_backstory_response_1", "I could use a man of your talents in my company"),
  ("npc8_backstory_response_1", "I should kill you where you stand for outrage."),
  ("npc9_backstory_response_1", "I need confident companions in my army if I am to achieve all I aim to achieve. Your love of riches will be well taken care of as well."),
  ("npc10_backstory_response_1", "I could use your strength, if you will fight for me?"),
  ("npc11_backstory_response_1", "I do quite a bit of travelling by sea, I could use you in my party."),
  ("npc12_backstory_response_1", "You're a bit nuts but if you like fighting you can fight for me?"),
  ("npc13_backstory_response_1", "While you are not on the front line, I could use you in my army if you are available?"),
  ("npc14_backstory_response_1", "Speed and accuracy are welcome in my party."),
  ("npc15_backstory_response_1", "Just so long as you are useful on the battlefield I am happy to hire you."),
  ("npc16_backstory_response_1", "You sound like you have great resolve and if you are available you can come into my service?"),
  ("npc17_backstory_response_1", "I run an adventure company and I will be travelling around the entire world so if you care to join us you will get the information you need."),
  ("npc18_backstory_response_1", "If it is adventure you seek then you may be keen to know that I lead an adventure party."),
  ("npc19_backstory_response_1", "I am feeling generous so I will allow you to join my party."),
  ("npc20_backstory_response_1", "You know you can be even more successful if you fight for me, I plan to leave no stone of this world unturned."),
  ("npc21_backstory_response_1", "Maybe you can release your fury fighting for me, maybe it will help you get back to your old self."),
  ("npc22_backstory_response_1", "There will always be threats to any nation, what brings you to this tavern?"),
  ("npc23_backstory_response_1", "Well if there is still some drive in you I could lead you on one last adventure."),
  ("npc24_backstory_response_1", "Well instead of following us when you see us why don't you join us?"),
  ("npc25_backstory_response_1", "I could use a good trainer in my crew."),
  ("npc26_backstory_response_1", "I know you are not a mercenary, but if you join my company as a friend you will soon get back your strength as well as obtaining the wealth you speak of."),
  ("npc27_backstory_response_1", "Your thirst for a fight will be quenched if you follow my leadership."),
  ("npc28_backstory_response_1", "Sounds like you lost everything. I could use the skills of a Lord in my army, it could be a new start for you?"),
  ("npc29_backstory_response_1", "Very interesting."),
