  ("npc1_backstory_response_2", "No way, I don't want to worry about having my head chopped off because you disagree with my leadership"),
  ("npc2_backstory_response_2", "Maybe another day Felix the poet"),
  ("npc3_backstory_response_2", "I do not need a bodyguard I am afraid Jalil, but I wish you luck for the future."),
  ("npc4_backstory_response_2", "A passive orc, I have seen it all now. So long."),
  ("npc5_backstory_response_2", "My party requires a higher moral code than what you aspire to."),
  ("npc6_backstory_response_2", "I can't risk you leaving at a bad time and ruining my plans."),
  ("npc7_backstory_response_2", "I do not need your skills right now but I will remember you when I do."),
  ("npc8_backstory_response_2", "Do you know who you just tried to steal from?"),
  ("npc9_backstory_response_2", "I feel your influence on my army would not be a positive one so I will continue my search for new companions."),
  ("npc10_backstory_response_2", "I don't intend to always be at war. Maybe you would be better off raiding with bandits."),
  ("npc11_backstory_response_2", "That sounds like a terrible state of affairs, I hope you fail."),
  ("npc12_backstory_response_2", "Move aside you insane freak of nature."),
  ("npc13_backstory_response_2", "Well when you invade another land this is what happens."),
  ("npc14_backstory_response_2", "I am not sure you are right for my company."),
  ("npc15_backstory_response_2", "You may have knowledge but I have no need for a horse archer."),
  ("npc16_backstory_response_2", "Good for you Skeezle, I wish you all the best."),
  ("npc17_backstory_response_2", "They probably left to get away from you Scarloc you monotonous bastard."),
  ("npc18_backstory_response_2", "Yes well there is not alot I can do about that."),
  ("npc19_backstory_response_2", "If it is safety you seek then believe me when I say that you would do well to avoid travelling with me."),
  ("npc20_backstory_response_2", "Very impressive, just don't try to steal any of my treasure or you'll wish you never came here either."),
  ("npc21_backstory_response_2", "A terrible tale, I am glad you got your revenge. Farewell."),
  ("npc22_backstory_response_2", "If I remember rightly, Lustria invaded the Old World not too long ago. Don't dish what you can't take."),
  ("npc23_backstory_response_2", "Thanks for the drink old man, farewell."),
  ("npc24_backstory_response_2", "If I catch you following me again my troops will take you prisoner."),
  ("npc25_backstory_response_2", "I can train my own men just fine."),
  ("npc26_backstory_response_2", "Like me you have big plans Uggluk, but maybe you should learn from your defeat."),
  ("npc27_backstory_response_2", "There is no space in my party for a man like you."),
  ("npc28_backstory_response_2", "I heard that curiosity killed the cat, looks like with you it rose again."),
  ("npc29_backstory_response_2", "That was interesting, but I have to go."),
