  ("npc1_signup", "That is settled then, we will drink brew and crack skulls together."),
  ("npc2_signup", "I am honoured to fight at your side {reg33?madame:sir}."),
  ("npc3_signup", "Excellent, you can count on me and you will find me relatively cheap when there are many half as good as me that go for twice the price."),
  ("npc4_signup", "I am always happy to be where I am valued."),
  ("npc5_signup", "Wisdom you have, and money also."),
  ("npc6_signup", "Excellent, if you are not already aware of my abilities I can assure you you will not be disappointed."),
  ("npc7_signup", "Then I am ready to join you and don't fail to use my knowledge when planning a siege, the faster a siege is won the less chance of a relieving army interfering."),
  ("npc8_signup", "You could try but I will escape your grasp, I am faster than you think, peaky or not. If you are smart you would hire me instead of attack me, make the most of my talents."),
  ("npc9_signup", "Good. Put me in a unit with some of my Venators and you will see a green field turn red."),
  ("npc10_signup", "I could fight for you if I knew you were serious and not just looking to use me for one important mission and then settle down like others have done. If you do I will kill you as I killed them."),
  ("npc11_signup", "I am used to only serving the mighty rulers of Naggaroth but I suppose I could join you to pass the time."),
  ("npc12_signup", "Mish mash Brrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrgash, Bug will fight again."),
  ("npc13_signup", "When I am on extended times of rest the Lady often comes to me in visions and instructs me on what we should do. It has been so long now I am worried she will not come, maybe I enter the field of battle once more and show her I am still worthy."),
  ("npc14_signup", "I would be pleased to ride with you."),
  ("npc15_signup", "I am very grateful for this opportunity. I have great knowledge on all races and cultures so if you wish to find a diplmatic solution rather than the sword then I will be happy to advise."),
  ("npc16_signup", "I joined an adventure party before and I wasn't much use on the battlefield. I promise it will be different this time."),
  ("npc17_signup", "I am not used to travelling in large groups of strangers but if you travel as much as you say then it would be a good idea for me to join you."),
  ("npc18_signup", "Really! Well you'd better know how to show a girl a good time or I won't be hanging around."),
  ("npc19_signup", "Oh  thank you, thank you. I have met some really nasty characters since I got lost I am afraid to travel out on my own."),
  ("npc20_signup", "I can handle things myself, I can fight alone or as part of a team. I have missed some companionship I must admit."),
  ("npc21_signup", "If you promise me we will fight some Goblins I will follow you where ever you go."),
  ("npc22_signup", "Revered Old Blood took control of my unit to use as his bodyguards and he didn't give me a new assignment."),
  ("npc23_signup", "It will take me a while to get back to my old form but why not?"),
  ("npc24_signup", "You do seem to travel a lot for an adventuring party which is good for me."),
  ("npc25_signup", "You will see the difference in your men in no time."),
  ("npc26_signup", "Well I suppose I need to start somewhere on the road to regaining my prime."),
  ("npc27_signup", "Then I will join you, just keeps the battles coming and I will stay with you."),
  ("npc28_signup", "Lost everything I did. I was nearly killed when I returned to the Empire and you can be sure I want nothing to do with the Tomb Kings. I am stuck but you are offering me a way out."),
  ("npc29_signup", "I will join you if you are the one to give me what I seek."),
