  ("npc1_signup_2", "Just don't let me down or I will squash you like a greenskin."),
  ("npc2_signup_2", "Just don't forget to stop off in the odd tavern or two on our journeys."),
  ("npc3_signup_2", "I am great in a siege too, just give me a view to the ladder and half the invaders will fall I swear it."),
  ("npc4_signup_2", "My healing hands are your healing hands."),
  ("npc5_signup_2", "My blade will shriek to your bidding."),
  ("npc6_signup_2", "I live to eradicate evil, to vanquish all my foes with pistol and with sabre. Now your enemies are my enemies, if only for a while."),
  ("npc7_signup_2", "While I worked for Borgio I never lost siege, they all starved, fell or surrendered. I hope to maintain the same record with you."),
  ("npc8_signup_2", "I am an excellent thief and finder of treasure and I know the halfling herblore so I can perform some basic healing as well."),
  ("npc9_signup_2", "I enjoy war so try not to bore me by having extended periods of peace. You may pay me but I still expect to have a good time."),
  ("npc10_signup_2", "They say that money is the way to tell how serious most employers are so I will require a sum which signals your intentions."),
  ("npc11_signup_2", "I will need to keep my combat skills in practice for when I am called back so an agreement between us would be mutually beneficial. I will warn you now that when I am called for I will leave immediately."),
  ("npc12_signup_2", "Waaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaagh!."),
  ("npc13_signup_2", "I can't go back to the King without good news, I wouldn't dream of failing him so fighting for you could be the answer to my situation. I just hope you are an honourable leader, I will not serve a tyrant."),
  ("npc14_signup_2", "No enemies will slip past me."),
  ("npc15_signup_2", "If you ever decide to start up your own kingdom, I would also make an excellent advisor although I will have to prove that to you with time."),
  ("npc16_signup_2", "My polearm training means I can inflict terrible damage on the enemy, even those great horses they ride."),
  ("npc17_signup_2", "I am the best you will find with a bow, I cannot stress that enough. You don't need to worry about me on the battlefield."),
  ("npc18_signup_2", "Don't think that because I am a girl you can take advantage of me. I know all the tricks and more. And if you ask me even once to make you some salmagundi I will cut your balls off."),
  ("npc19_signup_2", "Amazonian sisters are notorious for being tough but I am not. I regret not training with the others by I have been too busy pining after my true love. If you see Florin please let him join us, I miss his pretty face."),
  ("npc20_signup_2", "I have had some great moments it would have been nice to share with another so I think I will join you although I must get my fair share of the treasure."),
  ("npc21_signup_2", "Yes I will join you, my axe is not finished yet."),
  ("npc22_signup_2", "I have taken it upon myself to scope out the lands and learn more about the invading forces."),
  ("npc23_signup_2", "I may be old but with a bottle of rum in me I am as good as new."),
  ("npc24_signup_2", "I also think you could use my knowledge so I will accept your offer."),
  ("npc25_signup_2", "Let me get my things together."),
  ("npc26_signup_2", "Just so long as I go as your equal, as your friend. I know you are paying me but I am no servant and I deserve as much respect as you."),
  ("npc27_signup_2", "Just leave me to it on the battlefield."),
  ("npc28_signup_2", "I was never strong in battle but I am a great rider and am good with a lance. Put me in your cavalry and I will put on a good show."),
