  ("npc1_morality_speech", "Listen here {playername}. I did not join this company to be led by someone who {s21}. Make sure you do not do it again or we will fall out."),
  ("npc2_morality_speech", "{reg33?Madame:Sir} -- I'm not altogether happy that we {s21}. To accept a quest is like an oath and you should make sure it is seen through. I trust you will not let this happen again."),
  ("npc3_morality_speech", "Perhaps it is not my place to say so, {reg33?madame:sir}, but I confess that I am somewhat shocked that we {s21}. Of course I realize that war is cruel, but there is no need to make it more cruel than necessary."),
  ("npc4_morality_speech", "Excuse me {reg33?Madame:Sir}. I am happy to serve you but not if we {s21}, I do not wish to be associated with this kind of action. I am quite alarmed."),
  ("npc5_morality_speech", "If someone gives you a job then you must complete it. This is a first principle. You should not {s21} as it makes you look weak."),
  ("npc6_morality_speech", "Why did you attack those innocent people? This does not look good for your character when you {s21}, I suggest you be very careful."),
  ("npc7_morality_speech", "I was not pleased that you decided to {s21}. You have responsibilities to your men, if you want respect see that they are fulfilled."),
  ("npc8_morality_speech", "{playername} It is a bit much that you {s21}. I know I am guilty of the odd criminal act or two but that is just thieving. What you are doing is crossing the line."),
  ("npc9_morality_speech", "Some may complain that you {s21} but I don't think you should care, I wouldn't."),
  ("npc10_morality_speech", "Yes {playername}, this will please the Gods. Next time we leave no one alive, not even the children."),
  ("npc11_morality_speech", "I know much more than you about how to be a successful leader and I can tell you now that {s21} is not the way to win the respect of you troops. I know you are relatively new to this but you should know better. I am embarrassed to be led by you."),
  ("npc12_morality_speech", "Bug likes {s21}."),
  ("npc13_morality_speech", "I must protest most vigorously against you {s21}. No honourable leader would actively encourage such an action. I pray you do nothing of the sort again."),
  ("npc14_morality_speech", "I urge you to forget the fact that you {s21} captain. Some might get annoyed but you tried your best which is all one can do."),
  ("npc15_morality_speech", "{reg33?Madame:Sir} -- just so you know my opinion, any commander with sense will not let his company {s21}.I hope you don't mind me speaking so bluntly."),
  ("npc16_morality_speech", "{reg33?Madame:Sir}, We just look weak if we {s21}, we don't want to look weak now do we?"),
  ("npc17_morality_speech", "As our leader you should not encourage us to {s21}. Whatever the danger we must face it, not run and hide like halflings."),
  ("npc18_morality_speech", "No captain this is not the way to lead. What are you thinking {s21}, looks like your brains are a tiny as your balls."),
  ("npc19_morality_speech", "You know I don't know much but I have heard that {s21} is not a good thing. Maybe you should stop doing it."),
  ("npc20_morality_speech", "Sometimes you just can't do what people ask you to do captain. It is a tough world and things can prevent even the very best from seeing things through. Do not be disheartened for you will make ammends."),
  ("npc21_morality_speech", "It's a damn shame that you made us {s21} {playername}. We should stand up to our enemies in future."),
  ("npc22_morality_speech", "You should be more careful that {s21} doesn't happen again captain. It doesn't reflect well on any of us."),
  ("npc23_morality_speech", "I know I am hardly the, hic, paragon of righteousness captain. But in future you should not {s21}. That's a low thing to do, either sober, hic, or drunk."),
  ("npc24_morality_speech", "When I joined you {reg33?Madame:Sir} I didn't think that I would be party to {s21}. I am not happy seeing this happen so I urge you to not allow it to happen again."),
  ("npc25_morality_speech", "You really should take care not to {s21} captain. You have a responsibility, please don't forget it."),
  ("npc26_morality_speech", "Looting is just a fact of life isn't it captain. Some people kick up a fuss about it but so many Lords do it so why shouldn't we."),
  ("npc27_morality_speech", "Unless you want me to break you in two I suggest that you never {s21} again."),
