  ("npc1_retirement_speech", "You have tried your best to find the greatest opponents but I need a greater challenge to fulfil my destiny. I will now leave your company and head to the darkest tombs of Nehekhara in search of a worthy foe."),
  ("npc2_retirement_speech", "{reg33?Madame:Sir}, it has been a honour to serve you, but I must admit that my writing has been deeply neglected since I have been in your company and I have so much to put down from memory. So I must return home and begin my works. Maybe when I am done I will see you again."),
  ("npc3_retirement_speech", "It has been an honour to protect you it really has. However I am concerned at how slack the bodyguards in our realm are getting at the moment. There have been 15 successful assassinations of high ranking figures in the last 3 months and this is unacceptable. It is my duty to return and persuade them to take me back. I hope you understand."),
  ("npc4_retirement_speech", "It has been my life's honour serving in your company {reg33?Madame:Sir}, but the time has come for me to return to my homeland. I have learnt enough from you to stand up for myself so now I will return and hopefully show my kin that there is more to know than how to bash and crack skulls."),
  ("npc5_retirement_speech", "You have paid me well and I have gained much fame fighting for you for which I am grateful. Yesterday I received a message from Thanquol himself that he wishes me to become his personal assassin, this is a position I cannot refuse. I leave now, we shall not meet again."),
  ("npc6_retirement_speech", "Word has reached me that the Witch Elves are planning on returning to the Old World. I don't know much but I must leave at once for Fort Balderick and begin discussing our response."),
  ("npc7_retirement_speech", "I have served you faithfully and I wish you well for your future. However I must return to Miralgiano and summon my my men to me so I can assess our strength and start working as one unit again."),
  ("npc8_retirement_speech", "As fun as this conquering malarky is I miss the pleasures of being my own entity, doing what I want when I want. My chances to pilfer are getting less and less so I need to go back to my roots and return home."),
  ("npc9_retirement_speech", "I am bored so I am off, you are not the most boring leader I have ever followed but even so, you could have been a bit more aggressive than you have been."),
  ("npc10_retirement_speech", "I have received a calling from my Gods to return back home and raise an army in preparation for a great message I will receive on the top of Mount Vanir. I will leave you now."),
  ("npc11_retirement_speech", "The time has come captain for me to return as head of my fleet and prepare to launch a full scale assault on the seas. Serving you has been more enjoyable than I thought and if you need a favour in the future let me know, just don't interfere with my plans."),
  ("npc12_retirement_speech", "Boo."),
  ("npc13_retirement_speech", "{reg33?Madame:Sir}, I have been called to join the crusade by my King the majestic King Leoncouer. I am bound to leave at once but I admire you greatly and hope to see you again."),
  ("npc14_retirement_speech", "As happy as I am under your leadership {reg33?Madame:Sir}, the time has come for me to leave your side. Recently the call of my people has been stronger than it usually is, I feel it is time to put down my bow and return home where I can practice more gentle arts. Come and see me again one day, you will always be welcome."),
  ("npc15_retirement_speech", "I appreciate that you took me on but my advancement of knowledge has slowed down and I really need to begin my studies again. I will travel to the great Imperial library to study the Wood Elves as I know least about them of all the races."),
  ("npc16_retirement_speech", "Captain I have learnt alot under your leadership and am a much better fighter now than I was when I joined. I must leave though to spread my seed and create children from whom to pass on my skills. Farewell Captain and maybe I will join you again."),
  ("npc17_retirement_speech", "We both knew this time would eventually come and it has indeed arrived. I have documented all I need to know about the mass immigration and must now return home and report to my King. It was an honour to serve you."),
  ("npc18_retirement_speech", "I had been having so much fun that I forgot that my new ship would be ready. It is time I went back and rallied my crew for new adventures. I hear the Dark Elves are up to something well I say bring it on."),
  ("npc19_retirement_speech", "We have passed my home a fair few times since I joined you and now I think it is time I went back to my sisters."),
  ("npc20_retirement_speech", "I am moving on now to go adventure on my own. I thank you for your company but I have much to do. Farewell my friend."),
  ("npc21_retirement_speech", "Well Captain. The furnace inside me has died down and it is time for me to go back to my business. You can come drink with me any time and on the house for sure, it has been a pleasure fighting with you."),
  ("npc22_retirement_speech", "Word has reached me that my unit is to be placed back under my command so I must leave immediately. Farewell and thank you."),
  ("npc23_retirement_speech", "I am an old man captain and need to retire. It has been an honour serving you in my twilight years."),
  ("npc24_retirement_speech", "Captain, I have received word that my sister is very ill and there is no one to care for her since my brothers have all gone off to war. I must leave immediately and look after her, family must come first."),
  ("npc25_retirement_speech", "Captain, like all men there comes a time to retire and for me that time has come. I have been in the fighting business for a long time now and the time has come for me to step down. I will go back to the pits and make some money betting on the fights, no one knows the fighters better than me so I expect to be rich in no time."),
  ("npc26_retirement_speech", "Well my friend. The time has come for me to go forth and claim my kingdom. I know I said I wanted your help but you have your own mission and this is something I must face with my own army. Goodbye {playername}."),
  ("npc27_retirement_speech", "I need to kill bigger monsters and claim greater treasure than I have recently. Your army was fun for a while but now I am bored."),
  ("npc28_retirement_speech", "I have busied my mind with your campaigns for a long time now and I am grateful for the opportunity but I need to try and figure out how to reverse this curse so I will go to Nehekhara and see what I can discover."),
  ("npc29_retirement_speech", "I've grown tired of serving under you."),
