  ("npc1_rehire_speech", "You again. I have killed many Bone Giants since we last met and I am ready to kill again. If you are leaving soon I will rejoin you, just find stronger enemies this time."),
  ("npc2_rehire_speech", "{reg33?Madame:Sir}! It's good to see you again. Word has reached my ears of your exploits since I left and it made me miss it very much. Will you have me back?"),
  ("npc3_rehire_speech", "I found a new master to protect but he was an intolerable immoral fool and I was wroth to save his life. I almost missed a shot deliberately but I held my emotions in and I quit to save my reputation. I would much rather be under your service again?"),
  ("npc4_rehire_speech", "Hello {reg33?Madame:Sir}. I have travelled far but still you are the only one who is willing to accept my valuable skills. I have been getting very depressed with life recently, if you rehire me I will be even better this time around, even in battle."),
  ("npc5_rehire_speech", "You want to rehire me again?."),
  ("npc6_rehire_speech", "Greetings {playername}, it has been a while but if you wish for me to return to help your cause I will."),
  ("npc7_rehire_speech", "It may just be the drink talking but I wouldn't mind rejoining your party, what do you say?"),
  ("npc8_rehire_speech", "Hello again {playername}, being your companion is actually more fun than I previously admitted. Shall we let bygones be bygones?"),
  ("npc9_rehire_speech", "You are a laughable leader but I could do with a good laugh so I will rejoin you."),
  ("npc10_rehire_speech", "I am available again if you want my strength."),
  ("npc11_rehire_speech", "Captain! While I am still angry at you I like your tendency to force an issue with the enemy. If you want me back I will come but try and be a better leader this time."),
  ("npc12_rehire_speech", "Waaaaaagh! Let us fight again."),
  ("npc13_rehire_speech", "Our paths cross again {playername}. I left before as I felt you did a dishonour to the virtues I live my life by. I do however believe in redemption and word has reached my ears of some good deeds performed by your hand since we have parted. Maybe your company is a worthy place for me after all."),
  ("npc14_rehire_speech", "Well {reg33?Madame:Sir}, I made no secret of my disappointment last time I was in your employment. I did not think we would work together again but I must confess that the distances and locations we travelled to were thrilling, especially for one who likes to see as much of nature as I. If you require my bow once more then it is yours."),
  ("npc15_rehire_speech", "Why hello, {playername}. I can't say I'm entirely displeased to see you. You see, I took on another contract with another adventurer but he was a bigot and a tyrant so I left as soon as possible. It would be a great relief to return to your party."),
  ("npc16_rehire_speech", "Master, it is good that I have bumped into you. After I left you before I thought I was ready to return home, I thought I was trained enough to get vengeance on those who tormented me and to prove myself as a strong skaven. Alas I was wrong as I was beaten by robbers on the path to the border, I guess I have more to learn. I beg you to take me back and teach me some more, I need your help."),
  ("npc17_rehire_speech", "I have tried to relax since our last meeting but to have some form of combat mission to undertake is like an instinctual need for me. So if you want me in your company once more then I will come with you."),
  ("npc18_rehire_speech", "You're like a bad smell captain, or is Bastich here I don't know, haha, you can't keep away from me can you. As it is I need some excitement so what do you say we hit the road."),
  ("npc19_rehire_speech", "Captain! I thought I would do better without you but I was so wrong. Please take me back."),
  ("npc20_rehire_speech", "It seems our paths cross again. I was annoyed before but I forgive you for your poor judgement. We all have alot to learn you know so it's alright. You can welcome me back now."),
  ("npc21_rehire_speech", "We all say and do crazy things from time to time captain. I am sure if I come back things will work out this time."),
  ("npc22_rehire_speech", "Our paths cross again {playername} although things did not end well last time we were together. I still respect you as a leader and hold you in high esteem despite our disagreement."),
  ("npc23_rehire_speech", "You want me back?."),
  ("npc24_rehire_speech", "Have you noticed an increase in hostilities all over the world {playername}? I have had some close calls in areas I always felt perfectly safe in. I know we parted on unusual terms but if you would rehire me I will be grateful."),
  ("npc25_rehire_speech", "Good to see you again captain, I hear your troops have slacked a bit recently, you need me to whip them into shape."),
  ("npc26_rehire_speech", "You let me down last time you goat's anus, you should have respected my wishes. However I am still not ready to return to my home so if you need my help any time I am on your side."),
  ("npc27_rehire_speech", "You need Thrud then Thrud is ready to go."),
  ("npc28_rehire_speech", "Not many patrons want to drink with me any more. Is there any room left in your party?"),
  ("npc29_rehire_speech", "After traveling for a while, I realised my place is with you."),
