  ("npc1_home_intro", "I know the Chaos wastlelands very well, especially the north. If you know where to search and have the stomach for it then some of the deadliest creatures ever to walk the earth can be found in these parts."),
  ("npc2_home_intro", "We are near Altdorf, if we go in I must keep a low profile as they may still have not forgotten me. I will certainly never forget the city, it is where I first met Gotrek."),
  ("npc3_home_intro", "Can you smell that? Spiced incense, fresh fruit and the gorgeous smell of the tagine, it's the scent of Copher. I spent many a happy summer here when I was a boy, practicing archery and listening to the wise old men tell me tales of the past."),
  ("npc4_home_intro", "Begging your pardon {reg33?Madame:Sir}, but I thought you might like to know we are close to my home tribe in Gutrot."),
  ("npc5_home_intro", "I slew my first ever victim not far from here captain. The city of Skavenblight and its borderlands are dangerous areas. You need eyes on the back of your head."),
  ("npc6_home_intro", "This is the home base of my organisation in the New World. I have many men spread around the Empire waiting to return here when we have more news."),
  ("npc7_home_intro", "Power is such a fragile thing in Tilea, it is almost foolhardy to try and be a ruler as chances are you won't last too long in your position of riches and power."),
  ("npc8_home_intro", "We are near one of my lifes goals, Texcolo! Lustria is full of riches and it is rumoured that somewhere in Texcolo is a dungeon with an ancient treasure horde deep inside ."),
  ("npc9_home_intro", "We fought one of our greatest battles on this ground 5 years ago. About 50 of us had just finished a 3 day drinking session and the Empire must have got wind as they sent an army to ambush us, I imagine to catch us off guard and out of sorts."),
  ("npc10_home_intro", "The great men of the North are forever at war with each other; wars for supremacy, wars for pride and wars for blood."),
  ("npc11_home_intro", "Us Dark Elves have always been a seafaring race. Our corsairs haven't got the reputation they have for no reason and Lord Fellheart is the most feared of all the sea faring commanders."),
  ("npc12_home_intro", "Captain I feel slightly sober so I think now is the time to tell you that we are near my home of Stinkinz."),
  ("npc13_home_intro", "Hail the city of my King, the noble and majestic King Louen Leoncour."),
  ("npc14_home_intro", "Begging your pardon {reg33?Madame:Sir}, I thought I would mention that we are close to my home in Tor Elyr."),
  ("npc15_home_intro", "We are near my home of Tanis, a beautiful place and one of the unsung trade hubs of my people. I don't spend a lot of time there due to my travelling but there is a big place in my heart for my home."),
  ("npc16_home_intro", "My home master is a place called Putrid Lair near the frontline stronghold of Foul Peak."),
  ("npc17_home_intro", "We are close to my home and the forests which I have defended my whole life."),
  ("npc18_home_intro", "I was found here near Pirate King Fortress Captain. I say found because I don't know who my parents are or where I was actually born. I was abandoned on the deck of a ship when I was a baby and left for whoever would find me."),
  ("npc19_home_intro", "We are near my home and also the part of the jungle where I met Florin for the first time."),
  ("npc20_home_intro", "My birthplace {playername} is the Bretonnian castle of Bastonne."),
  ("npc21_home_intro", "Let me tell you about my home captain, my beloved brewery. It is large with the sound of machinery making a din at all hours of the day. The smell of alcohol and hops gets in your beard and in your clothes and there is always a merry atmosphere with much singing and joking by my workers."),
  ("npc22_home_intro", "We are near my home land of Xahutec, like most travellers I have not spent much time there in the last few years."),
  ("npc23_home_intro", "We are near my old home captain. I left my family 42 years ago to get pissed on the open sea. They must wonder where on earth I am, maybe I should go let them know."),
  ("npc24_home_intro", "We are near the quiet village of Middenstag My cousin is part of the international trade guild which is based here so I stay here whenever I need to rest in one place for a long time."),
  ("npc25_home_intro", "We are near my home of Mount Vanir where I was taught how to fight. My success here gave me a thirst for more so I decided it was best for my career if I moved to Mordheim and made my name there."),
  ("npc26_home_intro", "We are near aarvik, the first places I travelled to when I first came to this part of the world. The main force of the army I will raise will come from the chaos wastelands."),
  ("npc27_home_intro", "I was born near here. My mother abandoned me in a tavern and a group of mercenaries claimed me for their own."),
  ("npc28_home_intro", "I used to be the Lord of this here land. I was a good Lord, one who looked after his people and served the Emperor faithfully."),
  ("npc29_home_intro", "This reminds me of my home."),
