  ("npc1_home_recap", "I travel the world seeking out the mightiest foes in battle, that is all you need to know."),
  ("npc2_home_recap", "I am a merchant's son from Altdorf but fled after the tax riots. I am also a poet and am bound to Gotrek by oath after a nights heavy drinking."),
  ("npc3_home_recap", "I am a former bodyguard who is famed throughout Araby for never letting an assassin within close range of my master."),
  ("npc4_home_recap", "I am a skilled healer and surgeon from Gorrut camp who was disowned by my tribe for being weak. They seem to forget that my talents give strength to others who may have lost it."),
  ("npc5_home_recap", "I am a skilled assassin from Hellpit and I am an efficient killer. That is all you need know."),
  ("npc6_home_recap", "I am Mathias Thulmann and Master Witch Hunter. I am here to banish evil and to destroy the Witch Elves."),
  ("npc7_home_recap", "I am Braganza, elite mercenary at your service."),
  ("npc8_home_recap", "I am from the moot but I spend most of my time away so that I can borrow stuff from around the world."),
  ("npc9_home_recap", "I don't care about where I am from or you are from, all that matter is the here and now."),
  ("npc10_home_recap", "I am the Beorg, leader of the Bearmen of Urslo."),
  ("npc11_home_recap", "I am a Naval commander under the guidance of Lord Fellheart. My mission is to discover all I can about the pirates before we launch a sea invasion."),
  ("npc12_home_recap", "Brrtnik dnazt reeeeeeek."),
  ("npc13_home_recap", "I am from Couronne but am based in Lacombe currently while we prepare for the King's crusade against Araby and the Tomb Kings."),
  ("npc14_home_recap", "I am an archer and lover of horses, nothing too exciting {reg33?madame:sir}."),
  ("npc15_home_recap", "I am from the beautiful castle of Marrakech in the mighty Kingdom of Araby, and I am at your service."),
  ("npc16_home_recap", "I am a trained stormvermin and proud of it. I come from Putrid Lair but I will travel anywhere if it means I become a better fighter."),
  ("npc17_home_recap", "I am a protector of the Laurelorn forest alongside my group of hooded rangers. I was sent here by the King to try and find out with certainty the nature of the evil which has infected our forest and try to figure out what can be done for us to return."),
  ("npc18_home_recap", "The world is my oyster {playername} and I don't have time to call a place my home."),
  ("npc19_home_recap", "I am from the Amazonian rainforest and I got lost one day after being chased by giant snakes."),
  ("npc20_home_recap", "Not much that you do not already know. I travel around alot, I am never in one place for too long and I pay attention to the details in life."),
  ("npc21_home_recap", "I am a master brewer who brews the legendary Bugman's XXXXXX, the strongest and best tasting ale you will ever put between your lips."),
  ("npc22_home_recap", "In truth I don't have a home Captain. I go where ever there are enemies of Lustria."),
  ("npc23_home_recap", "I am nothing but a pisshead captain, don't mind about me."),
  ("npc24_home_recap", "I come from the small village of Opolensk but the whole world is my home. I travel around discovering wonders and learning about other cultures."),
  ("npc25_home_recap", "Yes {reg33?madame:sir}. I am a retired pit fighting champion and trainer. Now I serve you and give your men the benefit of my knowledge."),
  ("npc26_home_recap", "I come from the Mountains of Mourn, far north of the chaos lands. I was defeated by my tyrant in a fight for the leadership but whilst most losers are eaten, I was lucky to escape. I will return when I am ready and knock him off his throne once and for all."),
  ("npc27_home_recap", "I am Thrud and I like to Kill! Death! Maim! Mutilate! Destroy!."),
  ("npc28_home_recap", "Home, don't talk to me about home."),
  ("npc29_home_recap", "I am from a place you probably haven't heard of."),
