  ("npc1_kingsupport_1", "It means nothing to me what you do or who you want to rule. I will support you if that is what you want but don't expect me to bend the knee."),
  ("npc2_kingsupport_1", "Well, {reg33?Madame:Sir} -- I'd support you. I think you'd give the people the kind of enlightened rule which they have long needed."),
  ("npc3_kingsupport_1", "It would be an honour to once again protect a great ruler, of course I will support you. "),
  ("npc4_kingsupport_1", "Well, {reg33?Madame:Sir}, I think that you would be the kind of {reg33?Queen:King} that good souls such as myself would be proud to follow into battle..."),
  ("npc5_kingsupport_1", "A King you say, Kings pay better, I can support that."),
  ("npc6_kingsupport_1", "I cannot judge the legal merits of your claim. However you are a strong leader and do not hesitate to free the lands of undesirables, your people would be safe which is a rarity these days."),
  ("npc7_kingsupport_1", "So long as you know what you are getting yourself in for, that is alright by me."),
  ("npc8_kingsupport_1", "Sure thing, you could even make me treasurer? I will look after your coin."),
  ("npc9_kingsupport_1", "You want it, take it. You fight with me so you have a good chance, just remember who helped you get there when it comes out to handing out the riches."),
  ("npc10_kingsupport_1", "I don't care who is King or Queen of any land so if this is what you want I will indulge you this once."),
  ("npc11_kingsupport_1", "I would rather you were a foreign ruler than most of the ones we have now. You can have confidence that my influence will gain you significant support."),
  ("npc12_kingsupport_1", "Yes."),
  ("npc13_kingsupport_1", "That would be a fine thing, {reg33?my lady:sir}! Many is the tale of the hero who has proven their worthiness to wear a crown through valor. "),
  ("npc14_kingsupport_1", "I am usually suspicious of those who yearn for the highest power but in your case I will make an exception as you will make a very good ruler. "),
  ("npc15_kingsupport_1", "Well, you live by an honourable code, when you can, generally speaking. That's the best qualification for kingship there is, in my book. You show some respect for the rights of others too."),
  ("npc16_kingsupport_1", "Why not, captain? I'm sure you'd make a fine {reg33?Queen:King} -- and of course I'd hope you remember the little people like myself who fought for you on your scramble to the throne."),
  ("npc17_kingsupport_1", "I am no diplomat but I will do my best. I will head to Ulthuan to speak to my high elf cousins about you and your qualities which be fit a {King/Queen}. If the high elves accept you then others will generally be willing too."),
  ("npc18_kingsupport_1", "Fighting for a King sounds like fun, you can count me in. The pirates will listen to me and they will support your claim after of what I have to say."),
  ("npc19_kingsupport_1", "What little I can do, I will do it."),
  ("npc20_kingsupport_1", "You have to make your own luck in life and if yours is to take your place among the rulers of this world then good for you."),
  ("npc21_kingsupport_1", "Yes, Yes, one word from me and the citizens will speak well of your claim. I have celebrity, may as well use it."),
  ("npc22_kingsupport_1", "It is not what it used to be, being a ruler in this age. Before in the days of peace it was all pomp and luxury. Now it is nothing but war and protecting your borders. If that is the life you want then so be it."),
  ("npc23_kingsupport_1", "If that is what you want that is what you will get {reg33?Madame:Sir}."),
  ("npc24_kingsupport_1", "You will have my support and my advice too, you can trust me to help you in all matters of foreign diplomacy."),
  ("npc25_kingsupport_1", "To serve a {reg33?Queen:King} would be yet another honour I have brought to my family name. Of course I will help you."),
  ("npc26_kingsupport_1", "So the world has 2 new rulers to get used to, you and me, who would have thought it! Consider me a faithful ally."),
  ("npc27_kingsupport_1", "You want to be {reg33?Queen:King}, then you are a {reg33?Queen:King}, I wouldn't let anyone try and tell me different."),
  ("npc28_kingsupport_1", "You took me on when no one else would. Of course I will support your claim to be {reg33?Queen:King}."),
  ("npc29_kingsupport_1", "Why not, captain? I'm sure you'd make a fine {reg33?Queen:King} -- and of course I'd hope you remember the little people like myself who did you a pretty turn on your scramble to the throne."),
  ("npc30_kingsupport_1", "Why not, captain? I'm sure you'd make a fine {reg33?Queen:King} -- and of course I'd hope you remember the little people like myself who did you a pretty turn on your scramble to the throne."),
