  ("npc1_kingsupport_2", "If you must but don't be thinking I will tolerate you sitting around and playing dress up and talking your life away like other Kings do. You asked me to join you on the promise that we will seek battle against the best."),
  ("npc2_kingsupport_2", "Of course I will {reg33?Madame:Sir}, there are many lands which would benefit from a ruler like you. However if I am to do this then I must insist that you seek peace with the Empire, maybe even an alliance. We are surrounded by enemies and are constantly attacked some villages know nothing but war. I could not forgive myself if I supported the rise of another enemy of the emperor."),
  ("npc3_kingsupport_2", "By claiming rulership in this world you make yourself  a target for assassination. Many great Kings and leaders will seek to destroy you and I fear that so many will that I will not be able to protect you. Is such a move worth such a risk?"),
  ("npc4_kingsupport_2", "You would make a great ruler by anyone's account and if you wish they best for your people you could make me surgeon General and I can train a whole load of healers to help serve your army and your people."),
  ("npc5_kingsupport_2", "I will yes but you should secure the protection of your realm before you have claimed it by allowing me to open an assassin guild which will train many shaven to my bidding and thus your bidding."),
  ("npc6_kingsupport_2", "I will support you so long as you can assure me that any expansion through conquest will be made against the foul races and not the good, noble factions such as the Empire and the dwarves."),
  ("npc7_kingsupport_2", "Yes, captain, although be careful you do not bite off more than you can chew. Your army is small and your prestige small compared to the established King's of this world. You may find this move for power over before it is begun."),
  ("npc8_kingsupport_2", "I would -- on one condition. That one day you conquer the whole of Lustria and give me free reign to explore the dungeons and temples as much as I want. That sounds like fun."),
  ("npc9_kingsupport_2", "I might support you, just don't go getting all high brow and virtuous on me. Too many rulers try and act like their shit don't stink when they have a past which says otherwise."),
  ("npc10_kingsupport_2", "You want to be a King then be a King but don't be one of those Kings who spend their days with worrying about words and what is called intrigue. You fight for what is yours and what is not, or I will not support you."),
  ("npc11_kingsupport_2", "You will need to make a vow to me that you will not invest any effort in building a navy, the sea belongs to us and we cannot allow any new naval powers. Swear it and I will support you."),
  ("npc12_kingsupport_2", "Yes."),
  ("npc13_kingsupport_2", "Being a {reg33?Queen:King} is more than just leading an army, You need to conduct yourself and the affairs of state with the highest degree of honour and sensibility. I am not sure you are ready for such a responsibility, however many are rising who would make dreadful rulers and they may have the power to get their way. Maybe supporting you is the more prudent action, if you swear an oath you will be a just and honourable {King\Queen}?"),
  ("npc14_kingsupport_2", "I will of course support you although I have one request."),
  ("npc15_kingsupport_2", "I would. People might say that you don't have royal blood in your veins. But as far as I've seen, royal blood makes you a skinflint. Kings and nobles will take out loans or commission building projects without half a thought to how they're ever going to pay back all those commoners who expect to eat after an honest day's work. If you ask me, an honest tongue makes a {man/woman} a {king/queen}, not a fancy pedigree."),
  ("npc16_kingsupport_2", "I would be happy to sing your praises if you make me captain of your personal bodyguard? I would excel at such a distinguished position."),
  ("npc17_kingsupport_2", "I will support you if you support me. If this power which haunts our land is indeed Sylvania then their armies may rise against us in which case we will have to meet them in open battle. If this happens we will need allies, allies as strong as you......."),
  ("npc18_kingsupport_2", "It is a males dream to rule but I have always wanted my own little island somewhere which I can call my own and rule how I please. If I help you become {King\Queen} I hope one day you might grant me my wish."),
  ("npc19_kingsupport_2", ".Of course but if I could be so bold I would like to ask whether you could give me away at my wedding to Florin? Whenever that is of course, I am sure it won't be too long."),
  ("npc20_kingsupport_2", "Of course I can although maybe you can help me. I have paid back some debts to some less than friendly characters yet they are still trying to extort money from me under any pretext they can think of. I wish I never met them and I need them out of my life for the sake of my own safety and the sake of my bank balance. They are not the kind to listen to anyone but they may listen to a {King\Queen}, will you have a word with them."),
  ("npc21_kingsupport_2", "Support from the nobility will put your ship to sea but it is support from the common folk which keeps it afloat. If you want people to fight for you, work hard for you and speak well of you then their lives must be made the richer by being one of your subjects. If you tell them you will build infrastructure such as schools and roads and if you lower tax on beer so they can enjoy more of their favourite brew then I know many will be desperate to be under your rule, What do you say?"),
  ("npc22_kingsupport_2", "I can use my influence to gather support for your claim but you must swear never to invade my homeland. Support our sovereignty and I will support you."),
  ("npc23_kingsupport_2", "Aye Captain I will fall in and out of every tavern praising your name if wish. If you give me the money I will go do just that."),
  ("npc24_kingsupport_2", "So many want power but so little are willing to use it in a way which benefits their people and even less are willing to give the welfare of other nations any consideration. The world needs new international leadership, someone who can try and make all nations strive for a shared purpose."),
  ("npc25_kingsupport_2", "Where there is new power there is always war. Many factions will strike out against you if you declare yourself {King/Queen} of anything larger than a small hut."),
  ("npc26_kingsupport_2", "You wish to bargain for my support? Then I say I will do this if you support me. When I am ready to leave and take back my kingdom you will accompany me and help me win it back. You agree?."),
  ("npc27_kingsupport_2", "I want you to be {reg33?Queen:King} as that will mean more fights and more sieges. Enemies will rush to our gates which I like."),
  ("npc28_kingsupport_2", "I always thought I would follow no one but the emperor but there is no way he will allow me back into his confidence. If I have to follow someone else let it be you, but you must vow to be a loyal King."),
  ("npc29_kingsupport_2", "I will spread word about how you should be ruler to all in the land."),
