  ("npc1_kingsupport_2b", "Believe me I am not the only intolerable person in this conversation."),
  ("npc2_kingsupport_2b", "The Empire is no stranger to offensive wars or claiming land, I can make no such promise."),
  ("npc3_kingsupport_2b", "I can take care of myself maybe I had better ask someone more enthusiastic to speak in my name."),
  ("npc4_kingsupport_2b", "I need you here in my army at all times Oggy."),
  ("npc5_kingsupport_2b", "I can't be seen using skaven assassins as my personal tools of politics and influence. There would be uproar. "),
  ("npc6_kingsupport_2b", "No current King rules with such restrictions, look around you, every King takes whatever they can, I will not be an exception."),
  ("npc7_kingsupport_2b", "You underestimate me Braganza, Do not judge the politics of Tilea as the politics of all the Old World."),
  ("npc8_kingsupport_2b", "One doesn't simply conquer the whole of Lustria, It has to be one of the hardest places to take in the Old World, be reasonable.."),
  ("npc9_kingsupport_2b", "I will rule as I please."),
  ("npc10_kingsupport_2b", "I am no tyrant Beorg."),
  ("npc11_kingsupport_2b", "A navy has too much strategic value to just dismiss for such small a favour."),
  ("npc12_kingsupport_2b", "On second thoughts what good will you do!"),
  ("npc13_kingsupport_2b", "Oaths should be sworn to me, not the other way around."),
  ("npc14_kingsupport_2b", "Another time maybe, for now we march."),
  ("npc15_kingsupport_2b", "{reg33?Queen:King} of the Clerks, maybe, Enough of such talk"),
  ("npc16_kingsupport_2b", "If a day comes when I wish to forfeit my life I will be sure to make you captain of the guard."),
  ("npc17_kingsupport_2b", "My armies would be stretched too thinly Scarloc, there are many wars I must fight as well. Maybe the high elves will help you."),
  ("npc18_kingsupport_2b", "A whole island! You don't beat about the bush do you."),
  ("npc19_kingsupport_2b", "You are not my daughter so it would not be proper. Besides have you spoken to Florin about this."),
  ("npc20_kingsupport_2b", "Sort out your own mess."),
  ("npc21_kingsupport_2b", "A cut on beer tax, I wonder who would benefit from that! Nice try Bugman."),
  ("npc22_kingsupport_2b", "To openly favour the lizardmen could harm my chances to form good relations with other more influential factions. In order to protect my interests I must look to secure their friendships first and foremost so I will not swear this oath."),
  ("npc23_kingsupport_2b", "How can I expect to be taken seriously with a sozzled Bastich as my herald. Forget the whole thing."),
  ("npc24_kingsupport_2b", "There is no chance of any general accord being reached between all or even some of the leaders currently ruling at the moment. It is a wonder when any sort of treaty is signed between even two countries, let alone a few."),
  ("npc25_kingsupport_2b", "Let them come."),
  ("npc26_kingsupport_2b", "A whole army of ogres! That may be a bit too much for my troops."),
  ("npc27_kingsupport_2b", "Now you put it like that I better hold off."),
