  ("npc83_kingsupport_2b", "No thanks."),
  ("npc84_kingsupport_2b", "No thanks."),
  ("npc85_kingsupport_2b", "No thanks."),
  ("npc86_kingsupport_2b", "No thanks."),
  ("npc87_kingsupport_2b", "No thanks."),
  ("npc88_kingsupport_2b", "No thanks."),
  ("npc1_kingsupport_3", "I am no diplomat but I do know that a warrior king would be welcomed by many of the powerful families of these lands even if they would never admit it in public. Some of their lesser family members still drink in common taverns so I will gather some support for your claim through them."),
  ("npc2_kingsupport_3", "If you allow me to leave straight away I could be back within 2 weeks with news of significant support for your cause. I  still have the ear of many noble families back home."),
  ("npc3_kingsupport_3", "The people of Araby will never accept a {reg33?Queen:King} who does not believe in our religion. However they don't need to accept you, Just tolerating you will put you ahead of most other rulers out there. I know the writers of Araby's most prestigious papers. I will and get them to release some favourable articles about you."),
  ("npc4_kingsupport_3", "Then I will go and do my best to gain support for your claim. Not many people ever listen to me so I cannot promise success but if you command it then it is what I will do."),
  ("npc5_kingsupport_3", "While you are away at war you need eyes and ears closer to home to make sure you are not being targeted by malice or treachery. We can be the silent arm of your righteous judgment."),
  ("npc6_kingsupport_3", "Very well. I will leave right away."),
  ("npc7_kingsupport_3", "I will leave for a few weeks and I will gather news from my peers as to who is weak at the moment and will plant seeds of a new king rising who could be a potential ally to them. They will recognise you, whether you make an alliance or not is up to you."),
  ("npc8_kingsupport_3", "Good! Then give me a few weeks and I'll go back to the Moot, letting it be known that you're a {reg33?ruler:king} who respects the Halfings and their way of life. We are a wholly good peoples despite what some like to say."),
  ("npc9_kingsupport_3", "I can't offer you any help in the lands of Empire and Bretonnia but I have good relations with many prominent families in other factions of the Old World. So long as I persuade them you are no threat to their interests they will speak well of your claim."),
  ("npc10_kingsupport_3", "Good, then I will leave and will do whatever I can and whatever I please to make sure your claim has support."),
  ("npc11_kingsupport_3", "Good, You make your kingdom by land, I recommend taking the mountain territories and then expanding north. I will see what I can do to gain you support for your claim."),
  ("npc12_kingsupport_3", "Yes."),
  ("npc13_kingsupport_3", "Then give me leave for a few weeks, I am loyal to my King so I can only recommend you in certain terms but that will be enough for the nobility to approve, at least initially."),
  ("npc14_kingsupport_3", "I request that you lay aside any plans you have for world domination and be content with a reasonable size kingdom. Many rulers don't think of the cost in lives of troops and companions when they take on these wars of supremacy. So many generations have been lost and the prize, if ever achieved which is rare indeed, is never worth the sacrifice. Let your people know peace."),
  ("npc15_kingsupport_3", "I'm glad you think so. Here's what I suggest. I know men in the guilds here, and in the town halls, who've been shafted and shaken down until they can take no more. Here's what I'll tell them -- you're honest. You respect the rights of all classes. You'll pay your debts. You won't beggar your subjects."),
  ("npc16_kingsupport_3", "Excellent, that is good enough for me. I know you will make the right choice."),
  ("npc17_kingsupport_3", "Thank you {playername}, with this new alliance, this new strength, we can consider ourselves a step closer to salvation."),
  ("npc18_kingsupport_3", "Then I will redouble my efforts on the battlefield and use every gift I possess to try and establish you as a legitimate ruler."),
  ("npc19_kingsupport_3", "Thank you so much, What a wonderful day it will be. I am off to do my duty."),
  ("npc20_kingsupport_3", "A great weight has been lifted from my shoulders, thank you. I will now find my bards outfit and go sing about you in Leoncour's halls."),
  ("npc21_kingsupport_3", "Then I will write an article of support for your claim and stating your new policies and have it put up in all my taverns. That way the word will spread in most civilized countries."),
  ("npc22_kingsupport_3", "Very well then, I will help you. If you ever become a {reg33?Queen:King} then you could go even further and form an alliance with us, our armies are the toughest in the world."),
  ("npc23_kingsupport_3", "Excellent, I will be off then although I will miss out those skaven taverns. The beer always tastes strange there."),
  ("npc24_kingsupport_3", "The purpose of mutual co operation and mutual peace between all nations. We need an organisation which can speak for all and allow all agreements and disagreements to be discussed and negotiated openly between nations. This will prevent war and encourage understanding, you could head this organisation with my help."),
  ("npc25_kingsupport_3", "There is no ruler in this world who does not think that he has too many enemies and the last thing they need is another one popping up. They will try and crush you but with the right training and leadership your army can hold them off and prepare a counter attack which will make everyone fear you and think twice about attacking you again. Speak to me when I return and I will tell you how."),
  ("npc26_kingsupport_3", "Then the pact is sealed and we are now on our paths to glory and stature together."),
  ("npc27_kingsupport_3", "Just put me on the top of a siege ladder with hundreds of fodder running up at me and you will see my dream come true."),
  ("npc28_kingsupport_3", "I mean don't forget those who have supported you and fought for you on your journey to power. Don't betray those who deserve your respect like the Emperor and my peers have done me. We are all loyal to you {playername}, you will see your faith well invested."),
  ("npc29_kingsupport_3", "With your permission I shall go spread word of your right to be {reg33?Queen:King}."),
