  ("npc87_kingsupport_objection", "I don't support your decision to send them off to spread support."),
  ("npc88_kingsupport_objection", "I don't support your decision to send them off to spread support."),
  ("npc1_intel_mission", "There are not many people I want to see again but I do have a few contacts in {s17}, they would find it strange me asking as they know I don't care for gossip. They would not deny me though and if there is anything to be  found out about {s18} I will stay a for a few extra days of drinking as well."),
  ("npc2_intel_mission", "{reg33?My lady:Sir}, if you're interested in events in {s18}, I can still make contact with my old university {s17}. They're usually well-informed about political events."),
  ("npc3_intel_mission", "The publishing houses in Araby will know anything that could be known about {s18}, they make it there business to know as much as they can about anything. I will speak to my contact in  {s17} right away."),
  ("npc4_intel_mission", "I have healed a few warriors in my time who were grateful for my work, including some who fought in {s17}, they will most likely know about  {s18}. They say they owe me a debt, let's see if they are willing to repay it."),
  ("npc5_intel_mission", "If you like, {playername}, I can take a few days to visit my Eshin kin. They work in an underground network in {s17}, and hear the news from all across the {s18}. They may have some gossip about the feuds and rivaries of the great lords, if that is of interest to you."),
  ("npc6_intel_mission", "I have contacts everywhere, You need to in my line of work. I will seek information from the high council about {s18}, I will also get news of any signs of impending invasions. I will set off for {s18} immediately."),
  ("npc7_intel_mission", "I am familiar with {s17}, if there is anything pertinent to be learnt about {s18} then I will find out and return to you as soon as I can."),
  ("npc8_intel_mission", "If you have any interest in the events in the {s18}, a former priest-companion of mine retired and now keeps a farm near {s17}. He keeps in contact with a number of other old diplomats. I could visit him for a few days, and learn more about what is going on there."),
  ("npc9_intel_mission", "My Venators travel everywhere, we have men in nearly every tavern in the old world and as a consequence have made many friends over the years. If you want to know about {s18} then I will be sure to find out all there is to know in {s18} from one source or another."),
  ("npc10_intel_mission", "I will go to {s17} and find out all that needs to be known about {s18}, I will leave no one alive."),
  ("npc11_intel_mission", "Let me go and speak to my superiors in {s17}. They will know detailed information about {s18}, they may also be able to tell me when I will get my command back."),
  ("npc12_intel_mission", "Me sneak to {s17}. I hear talk of {s18}, me tell you."),
  ("npc13_intel_mission", "Word spreads fast in certain circles, especially in Bretonnia and if one desires news of {s18} then they should look no further then the prophetess sisterhood which is found in {s17}."),
  ("npc14_intel_mission", "Captain... I sell horses to the garrison of {s17}. One of their number has lately been in touch with me, and suggests that if I were to visit him, he could pass me information on events within the {s18}. I am willing to do this, if you can spare me."),
  ("npc15_intel_mission", "Captain. As you may know, I have for some time harboured a wish to go to {s17}, and study the masonry -- one of the finest examples of the older styles. As it happens, one of my colleagues is currently engaged there doing repair work on the curtain wall. While his sense of professional obligation I think would prevent him, rightfully, from disclosing to me any weaknesses in its defenses, I suspect that he would not be averse to offering up his opinion on the general state of the {s18}, if that is of interest to you."),
  ("npc16_intel_mission", "If there is one thing the Skaven can do well it is to spy on others and to find ways into places they should not. I will go and speak to the Eshin elders in {s17}. They will know about the goings-on in the {s18}."),
  ("npc17_intel_mission", "Information of this kind is best sought in Tilea. Mercenary captains and merchant Princes like to know everything as knowledge is often a bargaining tool in that part of the world. I will travel there and see what I can find out about {s18}."),
  ("npc18_intel_mission", "The hidden pirate coves in and around the region of {s17} are inhabited by the whisperers who trade in knowledge which they get from their teams of spies and moles all over the world. I will speak to them about {s18} and I know you will not be left disappointed."),
  ("npc19_intel_mission", "I will try and find out about {s18}, I don't really know how. Maybe I can go and speak to the sisterhood in {s17}, they might be able to find me."),
  ("npc20_intel_mission", "Bretonnians are not that knowledgeable on foreign affairs, I would be better off going to speak to my old guild. I will head for {s17} and see what they know about {s18}."),
  ("npc21_intel_mission", "There is nowhere better for over hearing important information than a Bugman's tavern. Alcohol can make even the most careful of tongues slip up, especially when my strongest brews are involved. I will head to my tavern in {s17} and prick my ears for any information about {s18}."),
  ("npc22_intel_mission", "We like to keep ourselves to ourselves so military intelligence is not our strong point but we opened a branch before the chaos invasion in case we have the need again. I will go and see them in {s17} and ask what they know about {s18} although I cannot say for sure I will find out anything of worth."),
  ("npc23_intel_mission", "Most pirates I know who would have that kind of information are dead. I know someone at {s17} who knows a lot about {s18} but he is 90 so I cannot vouch for his wits or his memory. I will go see him anyway."),
  ("npc24_intel_mission", "I know someone in {s17} who can help us although it will take me a fair few days to get there and back. It will be worth the trip though as they are sure to give me all they have on {s18} which should be everything."),
  ("npc25_intel_mission", "That kind of information will not come cheap but at least I know where to find it. There is a man in {s17} who can help us, he will give us all we need to know about {s18}."),
  ("npc26_intel_mission", "I will ask around, maybe in {s17} they will know something. I can't say I have ever needed this kind of information before but if you want updates on {s18} then there is the only place I can think to go."),
  ("npc27_intel_mission", "I will go to {s17} and break as many skulls as I have to until they tell me everything about {s18}. I won't be long."),
  ("npc28_intel_mission", "{s18} you say, that is easy enough. Well it is easy to find someone who knows, he is a good friend but whether he will tell me now is another thing altogether. I will head to {s17} and see if I have any good will remaining towards me."),
  ("npc29_intel_mission", "I could go to {s17}, to gather information about {s18}."),
