  ("npc18_woman_to_woman", "I hope your not worrying about the fact you are a women when it comes to receiving property from the King. If you smart you will end up with everything you want, you just have to think outside the box."),
  ("npc19_woman_to_woman", "Captain -- if you don't mind me saying, you've made quite a name for yourself in these parts. I suspect that if you were a man, a king would have offered you a fief by now. But foreign ladies should come to expect things like that. Men will find any excuse not to reward us for our work."),
  ("npc20_woman_to_woman", "{!}"),
  ("npc21_woman_to_woman", "{!}."),
  ("npc22_woman_to_woman", "{!}."),
  ("npc23_woman_to_woman", "{!}."),
  ("npc24_woman_to_woman", "Excuse me, {playername}. I would like to offer you my congratulations -- it seems that you are well on your way to making a name for yourself as a warrior to be feared. If you were a man, I suspect the kings of this land would be falling over themselves to make you their vassal. Alas, in this world, women like ourselves must fight twice as hard to receive what is only our due."),
